        "created_at": "2019-07-06T12:46:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"153217\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Isn\u2019t that plot called  La Goillotte? Have they had it renamed? Is that even possible?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Actually it was the Clos Frantin - IIRC Pinault bought the old Domaine du Clos Frantin cuverie and cellars from Bichot. The wine hog has a very thorough article about it: <a href=\"http://winehog.org/vosne-clos-deugenie-unknown-la-tache-neighbour-20071/\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Vosne-Romanee Clos d'Eugenie the unknown La Tache neighbour</a></p>",
